  </h2>


  <div class="content clearfix">
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1103810/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '1103810', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/spic/s2991700.jpg"/></a>
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1103810/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '1103810', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})" class="">
            柳文指要（上、下卷）
